China to Give Priority to Hydropower Development, 21st Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-23T02:54:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-23/china-to-give-priority-to-hydropower-development-21st-says.html
China  will give priority to
hydropower development in the five years through 2015, the 21st
Century Business Herald reported, without saying where it got
the information.  The nation will increase hydropower generation capacity to
around 284 gigawatts by 2015 and 330 gigawatts by 2020, the
newspaper said. Wind power capacity may reach 100 gigawatts by
2015 and 180 gigawatts by 2020, and solar power may rise to
about 2 gigawatts by 2015 and 20 gigawatts by 2020, according to
the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  